Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:04.43,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:05.92,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,敵 懼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.18,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.16,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,牙 眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.14,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.52,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,殺 滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:11.18,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,怪 凶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.38,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:32.79,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,這要 來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:35.36,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 還不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:41.01,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,大家退後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:49.01,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.47,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:53.73,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,凝視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.65,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,傾聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:00.27,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:03.11,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,水面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:05.32,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:06.99,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:18.79,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:21.92,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,回神了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.55,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:25.67,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:33.04,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是和他說的一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.39,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:39.06,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,自己默默承受一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:43.07,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,就會變成彆扭的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:45.54,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:50.32,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:08.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是不能勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:11.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 感覺輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,每天這樣會用光的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:25.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些螃蟹和牡蠣的屍體還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是食人族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的故鄉到底是個怎樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:33.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說了 妖精之鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是浮在遙遠的西海上的烏托邦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡鳥語花香 以下略
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妖 妖精地獄?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:46.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是地獄 是妖精之鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多你這種貨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:51.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾聽師傅大人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,位於西海裡傳說的島上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:56.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫斯基利格島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:59.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和靈樹森林一樣屬於狹間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,航海圖上沒有記載
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:05.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人也無法到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:10.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個島上有很多魔術師和精靈一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 史爾基妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個不情之請
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你能教我魔術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:26.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這又是哪一齣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾姐姐當魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從獸鬼的事以後 我一直在考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:41.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 你一個大人要當這個小毛孩的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:44.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候說實話我很觸動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:48.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你所引發的奇蹟 魔法的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也會有必須保護別人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:56.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給我勇氣的是卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:59.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和你給我的一把魔法短劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:03.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但那只是把銀刀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 就是如假包換的魔法短劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:08.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,芙羅拉說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接受巨大的謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在世界之中探求萬事萬物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:21.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有能照亮未知的黑暗的光明的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就請授予我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別盯著看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:31.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本來不是從出生就開始學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能很好的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且更關鍵的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:44.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人的年齡越大就越會被眼前的名為現世的世界觀束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:48.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將這種固有觀念打破是很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是遇到不少可怕事情的法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不用擔心這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己尚在修行中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也會力所能及地教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:10.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 法爾納塞小姐 要當魔女?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼趕快教我咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要從基礎開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 史爾基 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上的大海有點怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在散步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,確實在這月色下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不太容易入睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次看到大海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大海連通著幽界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,美麗又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕又恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣觸動扣人心弦的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的地方必定連接著幽界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候雖然也想像過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣站在海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:45.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才第一次明白師傅所言的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經踏上了無法回頭的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你太努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你那樣用小聰明去自己處理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然擔心他人也許能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時令你忘記自己的憂愁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這...這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從小就老這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,會變成世故的大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從我們魔術師來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:25.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和親人的生離死別和你們現世的人的含義不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對身處現世和幽界的魔術士來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡不是完結
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是羽化為新的偉大生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:39.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對 絶對不會悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總算好受些了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛和鼻子因為海風有點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也一樣 全身痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然在硬撐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 史爾基也長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:24.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒想到第一次的對象是這種大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡比自己大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:31.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但確實比那兩個強一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:35.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會對狂野大叔第一次敞開少女的青澀情懷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 心裡癢癢的 無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這話我原樣奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近欠了你不少人情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是現在才開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且先道個謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你這次有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛失去幾種顔色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,舌頭失去味覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,指尖顫抖疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:20.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你身穿那副甲冑作為狂戰士戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光明 聲音 溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:27.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你會失去許多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真不討人喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還是那樣無所不知的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再那麼狼狽的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我會讓你看到我好好用它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我不會讓那種事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,之前讓你多費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:59.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我失禮 你和師博大人是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:08.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這幅甲冑原本是你穿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是好友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有點像你們現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿在這甲冑上的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像絶不會熄滅的火焰一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算曾經控制住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火種也會繼續存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一有機會就會輕易地化為業火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有護符保護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你還想保有人的身份的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的親切關懷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:47.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼親切能不能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:53.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙 那些使徒何要襲擊婆婆的洋館
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:00.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹現在是現世之外的超然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:06.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難以想像現世有人能威脅他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:14.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就好比在故事中登場的人物要挑戰作者一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能挑戰鷹 要想威脅到他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有和他一樣是故事外的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個他就把師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:34.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一個魔法師比起千軍萬馬更讓他忌憚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:46.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們繼續旅程的話 很快就會再次和使徒碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後到那時 率領他們的恐怕就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他會來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要保護還是要挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就繼續追問你的靈魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以人類之軀矗立於狹間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一個希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要去的妖精之鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:36.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,名為 花吹雪王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,頗有力量而在傳說中傳頌的妖精王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是魔導書中被記載
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在很多的詩歌和故事中都有他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋 這種事一個字也沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:59.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,統冶巴克故鄉的是那樣的大妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:03.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,借助他的力量就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:08.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你的愛人烙印女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復本心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不說假話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,復原 她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:38.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的願望不一定完全是那個女孩期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:55.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 說起花吹雪王 就是在廣為傳頌的偉大的妖精王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厲害的嗎你們的王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼瞞著我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙難道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:17.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的願望不一定就完全是她的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:29.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,霧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著大霧 有什麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時一樣的死靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣 好久不練身體都鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:58.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這股氣 比起死靈更像入侵洋館的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:13:59.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:23.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓動物被某種靈附身做出來的魔法生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:25.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是統稱的使魔的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,依巴蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:39.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜是滿月 是最能發揮魔法威力的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:43.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不在寺院 也能施展四方之王陣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在法術發動之前 請拖延一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐 保護好卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生 你的身體還不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,活動活動遲鈍的身體正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這麼龐大也出不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用這東西餵飽它們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嚐嚐本大爺自創劍法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:29.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然看穿了我的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:32.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是照敵人嘴裡滾過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就是這個節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真強 完全復原了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑在嗅血的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在尋找爆發的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要意識混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將甲冑的力量最小限度發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:14.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是抑制疼痛讓身體活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,執掌韆繩的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 來了來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你趕緊幹點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:29.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,馬魯可圖 阿忒 蓋不魯 蓋德魯 魯 阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還是一如既往的華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚看起來很像極光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時這間屋子周圍安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:51.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對於有肉體的他們防壁的力量是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱大群怪物的施術者一定就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託趕快 大魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等 暫停 暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,追蹤氣流的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:17.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在海岸岩石背面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要逃趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 庫夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,霧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 趕緊離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比巨鬼還大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:15.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大的話 我的防壁防不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準眼睛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱它的術士在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大海之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼怪力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要是還要戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然厲害 面對那種大傢伙一點也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把你做成沙西米啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那樣傷口就又...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我來引導他回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,海吼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把我捲入深深的水底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,發出巨大轟鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:40.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,根據傳說 被稱為狂戰士的人不止敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己人都會感到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 那麼猛烈的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此 附近的一切都會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:55.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不問敵我 一同斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:11.20,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,看著很好吃 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.48,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,比耶卑斯風海味火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.24,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.62,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
